# Asset-slot drop zone — ENFORCES the ASSETS.md promise.
#
# Everything under public/arcade/** is a licensable / copyrightable drop-in slot
# (music, cover art, character models, SFX) loaded at RUNTIME with a graceful
# fallback. The repo must ship NONE of these files. This nested .gitignore makes
# that guarantee real: a stray `git add .` after the owner drops, say,
# rhythm-song-1.mp3 cannot accidentally stage/commit/redistribute it.
#
# Lives here (not the owner-owned root .gitignore) on purpose. Keep this file
# tracked so the directory + the rule persist even when no slots are filled.
*
!.gitignore
